    • Method Detail

      • add

        public static ElPollo.MemberOverride add(ElPollo.MemberOverride override,
                         java.lang.String... matches)
        Add a new override to the system.
        Parameters:
        override - A MemberOverride object specifying the source, override.
        The override object must be an instance of OverrideCustom.
        matches - When this is specified override will only be called when
        the method that calls source matches one of these items.
        can be one of method, class name or java package.
        Keep empty to not do any match checking.


        Examples:
        foo.bar.ClassName.func - must originate from method function in foo.bar.ClassName.
        foo.bar.ClassName - call must originate from class foo.bar.ClassName.
        foo.bar - must originate from java package foo.bar.
        foo.* - must originate from any package, class or function under foo.
        Returns:
        Returns the MemberOverride object.
        See Also:
        ElPollo.MemberOverride

      • remove

        public static void remove(ElPollo.MemberOverride override)
        Remove a previously added override
        Parameters:
        override - The override object used when adding the override.
